rmations\": 334,\r\n    \"spendable\": false,\r\n    \"solvable\": true,\r\n    \"safe\": true\r\n  }\r\n]\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n__EDIT__\r\n\r\nAnd just because I'm happy, this is the transaction made: 40f3ca2ef6dc8fc1b3648e612d63fda43d43fc5559d0b3f89e51b7a3bcc73865",
